title: 1000 Clasic PC games
description:
This is a collection of over 1000 PC games dating from around the release of Windows 3.1 up to about Win98. Some of these games can be run under WinXP/2000 and I am actually running five of them on my own XP system.

Some titles in this collection:

Dangerouse Dave
The Elder Scrolls (demo of the first game but full version is free on thier site)
Doom
Dungeons of Death
F18: No Fly Zone
Frogger Jr.
Galacta
Galaga 94
Jill of the Jungle
Joust
Maddog Williams
Mario
Mortal Kombat II (demo)
Spear of Destiny
Warcraft (demo of original)

This is a two CD setup that loads a program on your system to let you browse the games and then you put in the appropriate CD (it tells you what disk the game is on) to load the game.

Ther are two CD .iso files in this torrent.
